558
00:43:59,270 --> 00:44:00,380
Those are two different things.

559
00:44:00,380 --> 00:44:03,140
How? This is one thing.

560
00:44:03,140 --> 00:44:05,300
We can't let Siyu, such a good girl—

561
00:44:05,300 --> 00:44:08,030
