562
00:44:08,030 --> 00:44:09,550
Huh?

563
00:44:09,550 --> 00:44:11,590
You, you, you, you.

564
00:44:11,590 --> 00:44:15,350
Take the initiative to make peace. Then, you can start your happy life together.

565
00:44:19,520 --> 00:44:22,580
I can also give Xiaoling an explanation on my end.

566
00:44:22,580 --> 00:44:27,170
I will tell her that you don't have a mistress.

567
00:44:27,170 --> 00:44:30,890
You don't have the seven-year itch. You don't have a marriage phobia.

568
00:44:30,890 --> 00:44:32,530
